RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT a.product_code, a.product_description FROM oltms_product a, olvw_avl_prod_br_usr b WHERE a.module = 'FC' AND a.product_code = b.product_code AND b.branch_code = NVL(?,global.current_branch) AND b.user_id = global.user_id AND EXISTS (SELECT l.product_code FROM lbtms_facility_product l WHERE l.product_code = a.product_code AND l.participant_product IS NOT NULL)AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM oltms_product k, OLVW_USER_PRODUCTS S WHERE S.USER_ID = global.user_id AND S.PRODUCT_CODE = k.PRODUCT_CODE AND S.PRODUCT_CODE = b.product_code)ORDER BY a.product_code

select a.customer_no, b.short_name,B.CUSTOMER_NAME1 from olvws_product_customers a, oltms_customer b where a.product_code = ? and a.customer_no = b.customer_no and b.auth_stat = 'A' and b.record_stat = 'O' and not exists (select 1 from oltms_branch_parameters c where c.branch_code = ? and c.rounding_participant = b.customer_no) order by customer_no

select vw.ccy_code, ccy.ccy_name from olvws_product_currencies vw, cytms_ccy_defn ccy where vw.ccy_code = ccy.ccy_code and vw.product_code = ? and ccy.record_stat = 'O' and ccy.auth_stat = 'A' order by vw.ccy_code
select a.status, b.description from oltms_product_status_master a, oltms_contract_statuses b where a.product = ? and a.status = b.status_code and b.Status_type = 'C' order by a.status_sequence

select a.customer_no, b.short_name from olvws_product_customers a, oltms_customer b where a.product_code = ? and a.customer_no = b.customer_no and b.auth_stat = 'A' and b.record_stat = 'O' and not exists (select 1 from oltms_branch_parameters c where c.branch_code =? and c.rounding_participant = b.customer_no) order by customer_no
SELECT FIELD_DESC FROM OLTM_STATIC_FIELD_VALS WHERE FIELD_TYPE = 'WL' AND FIELD_NAME = 'WLREMARKS' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'

SELECT A.NAMED_AGENT,B.SHORT_NAME FROM LBTMS_NAMED_AGENT A,OLTMS_CUSTOMER B WHERE A.NAMED_AGENT = B.CUSTOMER_NO AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND B.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND B.AUTH_STAT = 'A'
SELECT ADMIN_ID, ADMIN_NAME FROM OLTMS_ADMINISTRATOR WHERE ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O'

RAD_SUMMARY.TITLE: LBL_BLK_FACILITY_SUMMARY
RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_MULTIBRN_WHERECLAUSE: Branch IN (SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVW_USER_BRANCHES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID INTERSECT SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMTB_USER_ROLE WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID UNION SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVWS_USER_CENTRAL_ROLES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID)

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM cytms_ccy_defn where record_stat = 'O' and auth_stat = 'A' AND ONCE_AUTH = 'Y'
SELECT FIN_CENTRE,FIN_CENTRE_DESC FROM OLTM_FIN_CENTRE WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A'
SELECT component, description, fee_rule from lftms_product_fee WHERE product_code = ? and stop_association = 'N'

select a.customer_no, b.short_name from olvws_product_customers a, oltms_customer b, TLTMS_POSITION_IDENTIFIER C where a.product_code = ? and a.customer_no = b.customer_no AND B.CUSTOMER_NO = C.PORTFOLIO and b.auth_stat = 'A' and b.record_stat = 'O' AND c.auth_stat = 'A' AND c.record_stat = 'O' and not exists (select 1 from oltms_branch_parameters c where c.branch_code =? and c.rounding_participant = b.customer_no) order by customer_no
SELECT distinct A.counterparty,A.cust_name FROM OL_LNVWS_CONTRACT_SUMMARY A ORDER BY A.counterparty
